===Noun===
'''diaper''' (''plural'' '''diapers''')

#(''US, Canada'') An [[absorbent]] [[garment]] worn by a [[baby]] who does not yet have [[voluntary]] control of its [[bladder]] and [[bowels]] or by someone who is [[incontinent]].

